{"title":"Python flask 環境安裝","uid":"36ba4d8002cc8c0e2f4cca291230c20b","slug":"Python-flask-環境安裝","date":"2021-05-01T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2022-06-13T14:16:00.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Python-flask-環境安裝.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"content":"<h2 id=\"1-Python-環境準備-MAC\"><a href=\"#1-Python-環境準備-MAC\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1. Python 環境準備 (MAC)\"></a>1. Python 環境準備 (MAC)</h2><p>我們要在 Mac 環境安裝</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Python3</li>\n<li>pip3</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"使用-homebrew-安裝-Python-3\"><a href=\"#使用-homebrew-安裝-Python-3\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"使用 homebrew 安裝 Python 3\"></a>使用 homebrew 安裝 Python 3</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-base\" data-language=\"base\"><code class=\"language-base\">brew install python</code></pre>\n\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>檢查目前 Python 的版本</p></blockquote>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-base\" data-language=\"base\"><code class=\"language-base\">python --version</code></pre>\n\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>如果顯示的版本是 Python 2，那麼試著下面的指令</p></blockquote>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-base\" data-language=\"base\"><code class=\"language-base\">python3 --version</code></pre>\n\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>看看是否是 Python 3</p></blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"確認-pip-是否安裝成功\"><a href=\"#確認-pip-是否安裝成功\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"確認 pip 是否安裝成功\"></a>確認 pip 是否安裝成功</h3><p>pip 是 python 的套件管理工具，但是並非等於 npm，更加類似於 mac 的 homebrew，或是 ubuntu 中的 apt install 這樣的工具</p>\n<p>這次我們要使用的 python 版本為 python3 ，所以要安裝 pip3</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-base\" data-language=\"base\"><code class=\"language-base\">pip3 install pipenv</code></pre>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Vx59LO4.png\" alt=\"image\"></p>\n<p>如果顯示的是 3.x 版本，是正確的</p>\n<p>如果不是的話，試著使用 <code>pipenv</code>，看看顯示的是否是 Python 3.x 版本而非 2.x 版本</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Ae1LvMJ.png\" alt=\"image\"></p>\n<p>原因在於 Python 2 已經停止維護，所以無論是 Python 的版本或是 pip 的版本，都需要使用 3.x 以上的版本。</p>\n<h2 id=\"3-安裝-pipenv-管理工具-通用\"><a href=\"#3-安裝-pipenv-管理工具-通用\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"3. 安裝 pipenv 管理工具 (通用)\"></a>3. 安裝 pipenv 管理工具 (通用)</h2><p>pipenv 可以看作是 node.js 中的 npm (Node Package Manager)</p>\n<p>然而實作上不太一樣，這是 python 獨有的背景與設計。</p>\n<p>但是使用方式跟 npm 很相似</p>\n<p>輸入安裝指令後</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-base\" data-language=\"base\"><code class=\"language-base\">pipenv install flask</code></pre>\n\n<p>開始安裝畫面</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Bhb2q39.png\" alt=\"image\"></p>\n<p>接著，我們看看資料夾多了什麼東西</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-base\" data-language=\"base\"><code class=\"language-base\">❯ ls\n01 installation.md Pipfile            Pipfile.lock       img</code></pre>\n\n<p>增加了兩個 Pipfile 與 Pipfile.lock \b 這兩個檔案</p>\n<p>輸入 <code>cat Pipfile</code> 後，即可發現剛剛安裝的 flask 已經安裝完畢</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/hLxAS1r.png\" alt=\"image\"></p>\n","text":"1. Python 環境準備 (MAC)我們要在 Mac 環境安裝 Python3 pip3 使用 homebrew 安裝 Python 3brew install python 檢查目前 Python 的版本 python --version 如果顯示的版本是 Python 2...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":830,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Backend","slug":"Backend","count":4,"path":"api/categories/Backend.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Backend","slug":"Backend","count":4,"path":"api/tags/Backend.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#1-Python-%E7%92%B0%E5%A2%83%E6%BA%96%E5%82%99-MAC\"><span class=\"toc-text\">1. Python 環境準備 (MAC)</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8-homebrew-%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%9D-Python-3\"><span class=\"toc-text\">使用 homebrew 安裝 Python 3</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%A2%BA%E8%AA%8D-pip-%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%9D%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F\"><span class=\"toc-text\">確認 pip 是否安裝成功</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#3-%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%9D-pipenv-%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7-%E9%80%9A%E7%94%A8\"><span class=\"toc-text\">3. 安裝 pipenv 管理工具 (通用)</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"Michael","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210313122054101.png","link":"/","description":"happy coding!","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/Michael0520","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"JavaScript-this","uid":"2036fc5e0715a4059c717df79605817f","slug":"JavaScript-this","date":"2021-05-12T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2022-06-13T14:05:56.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/JavaScript-this.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"text":"[JavaScript] this this 是什麼？ 圖片來源：What is this meaning of this? this 是函式執行時所屬的物件，其值是在執行時期做綁定，可大致歸納為四個規則以供判斷 判斷 this 的四個規則this 的值可用四種規則判斷： 預設綁...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"9.6k","symbolsTime":"9 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"JavaScript","slug":"JavaScrip